__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    GetAliasArray:
      path: /alias/array
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Returns an array alias
      response:
        docs: Array alias response
        type: list<string>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              - string
    GetAliasObject:
      path: /alias/object
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Returns an object alias
      response:
        docs: Object alias response
        type: AliasObject
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              foo: foo
              bar: 1
    GetAliasString:
      path: /alias/string
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Returns a string alias
      response:
        docs: String alias response
        type: string
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body: string
    GetAliasOptionalString:
      path: /alias/optional-string
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Returns an optional string alias
      response:
        docs: Optional string alias response
        type: nullable<string>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body: string
    GetAliasOptionalObject:
      path: /alias/optional-object
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Returns an optional object alias
      response:
        docs: Optional object alias response
        type: nullable<AliasOptionalObject>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              foo: foo
    GetDontResolveMe:
      path: /alias/dont-resolve-me
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Returns a don't resolve me alias
      response:
        docs: Don't resolve me alias response
        type: DontResolveMe
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body: string
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  AliasArray:
    docs: Alias for array of strings

  AliasObject:

  AliasString:
